title: Margaret Cho
itunes:title: Margaret Cho
description:
The legendary stand up comedian and actress Margaret Cho (30 ROCK, THE FLIGHT ATTENDANT, AMERICAN GIRL) is on the podcast telling Whitney about being a lazy Dominatrix, pee play, and human dog parks.  Margaret's podcast THE MARGARET CHO comes out Thursdays wherever you get your pods.  Go to https://margaretcho.com/ for tour dates.  Margaret's new movie FIRE ISLAND is streaming now on Hulu.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
